Package energy.usef.agr.workflow.plan.create.aplan

Classes for creation of A-plans in the plan phase by the Aggregator.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgrCreateAPlanPlanboardCoordinator
    Aggregator coordinator class interacting with the planboard in the 'Create and Send A-Plan' workflow.
    AgrUpdateAPlanPlanboardCoordinator
    Aggregator coordinator class updating A-Plan plan board messages.
    CreateAPlanEvent
    Event class that is used to trigger the workflow of creating and sending A-Plan.
    FinalizeAPlansEvent
    Event class that is used to trigger finalization of A-Plans.
    FinalizeAPlansEventTrigger
    Class in charge of the triggering of the UpdateAPlanEvent.
